"750ml bottle poured into a tulip. Aroma of funk, sour cherry, wine. Hazy reddish brown pour with a beige head that faded quickly, minimal lacing. Flavor of tart sour cherry, red wine, wood, subtle chocolate. Sourness lessened as it warmed in the glass. Finish is a touch hot. Nicely done."
